Software	Version	Purpose
RepeatModeler	2.0.7	Repeat library
RepeatMasker	4.1.7	Repeat masking
HISAT2	2.2.1	RNA-seq mapping
BRAKER3	3.0.8	Gene prediction
GeneMark-ETP	bundled	Gene prediction
ProtHint	bundled	Protein hints
AUGUSTUS	bundled	Gene prediction
CD-HIT	4.8.1	Protein clustering
BUSCO	5.4.3	Annotation completeness
eggNOG-mapper	2.0.1	Functional annotation
